---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Battle of Okinawa: 10 Realities You Never Know | Unmuting Ryukyu">

	<article>

		<!-- ARTICLE HEADER -->
		<header style="padding:72px 32px 56px;background:#1C2C4F;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:4px solid #8B1D25;">
			<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:5px;height:100%;background:#8B1D25;"></div>
			<div style="max-width:840px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;">
				<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;">
					<span style="display:inline-block;background:#8B1D25;color:#F0EBE3;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">Documentary</span>
					<span style="color:#8B9BB8;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:12px;">March 2026</span>
				</div>
				<h1 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(26px,5vw,44px);font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 20px 0;line-height:1.25;">Battle of Okinawa: 10 Realities You Never Know About the Worst War in History</h1>
				<p style="color:#8B9BB8;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:0;">By <a href="/about/" style="color:#D4C9BC;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Shohei Toguchi</a></p>
			</div>
		</header>

		<!-- ARTICLE BODY -->
		<div style="padding:72px 32px 96px;background:#F0EBE3;">
			<div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;">

				<!-- Video Embed -->
				<div style="background:#0a0a0a;margin-bottom:56px;box-shadow:4px 4px 0px #1C2C4F;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #D0C5BA;">
					<div style="position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;height:0;">
						<iframe style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2v2vOrz5RXA" title="Battle of Okinawa" allow="accelerometer;autoplay;clipboard-write;encrypted-media;gyroscope;picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Article Content -->
				<div style="font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;color:#4A3F3B;font-size:16px;line-height:1.95;">

					<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1C2C4F;margin:0 0 20px 0;padding-top:8px;border-top:2px solid #D0C5BA;">Introduction</h2>
					<p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
						The Battle of Okinawa, codenamed "Operation Iceberg," was one of the largest amphibious assaults in the Pacific Theater of World War II. Fought over 82 days from April 1 to June 22, 1945, it was a battle that changed the course of history — and devastated an entire island.
					</p>
					<p style="margin:0 0 40px 0;">
						But beyond the military history lies a human story that most of the world has never heard. This documentary explores 10 realities about the battle that reveal the true cost of war on the people of Okinawa.
					</p>

					<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1C2C4F;margin:0 0 20px 0;padding-top:8px;border-top:2px solid #D0C5BA;">Key Takeaways</h2>

					<div style="background:#fff;border-left:4px solid #8B1D25;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Reality 01</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.85;margin:0;"><strong>Civilian casualties outnumbered military casualties.</strong> An estimated 100,000 civilians — roughly one-third of the island's population — perished during the battle.</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#fff;border-left:4px solid #1C2C4F;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;">
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Reality 02</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.85;margin:0;"><strong>Okinawa was used as a strategic sacrifice.</strong> The island served as the final stepping stone before a planned invasion of mainland Japan, placing its people in the crossfire of two empires.</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#fff;border-left:4px solid #8B1D25;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:40px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Reality 03</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.85;margin:0;"><strong>The trauma continues today.</strong> The legacy of the battle shapes modern Okinawan identity, from the ongoing U.S. military presence to the preservation of peace memorials.</p>
					</div>

					<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1C2C4F;margin:0 0 20px 0;padding-top:8px;border-top:2px solid #D0C5BA;">Why This Story Matters</h2>
					<p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
						Understanding the Battle of Okinawa is not just about history — it's about understanding why peace is worth fighting for. The people of Okinawa carry this memory not as a burden, but as a responsibility to ensure it never happens again.
					</p>
					<p style="margin:0;">
						This is why we film. This is why we tell these stories.
					</p>

				</div>

				<!-- CTA -->
				<div style="margin-top:64px;background:#1C2C4F;padding:48px;border-top:4px solid #8B1D25;text-align:center;">
					<h3 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 14px 0;">Want to see more stories like this?</h3>
					<p style="color:#A8B8C8;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 28px 0;line-height:1.9;">Subscribe to our YouTube channel for new documentaries every month.</p>
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@letsgokinawa?sub_confirmation=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#8B1D25;color:#F0EBE3;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.05em;">
						<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
						Subscribe on YouTube
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Navigation -->
				<div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;">
					<a href="/blog/" style="text-decoration:none;color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.05em;">← Back to Blog</a>
					<a href="/videos/" style="text-decoration:none;color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.05em;">All Videos →</a>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>

	</article>

</Layout>
